title: Biochemical Oxygen Demand
summary: A small quantitative dataset of oxygen usage in microbes

title: Biomass of Herbiverous Fish
summary: Data on the biomass of deep and shallow Abobrinha Reef fish.  Has 3 categorical groups and many independent quantitative variables, some of which have missing values.

title: Bird Sightings in Texas
summary: A raw set of categorical timed observations of bird species. Requires summarisation and is annotated to different levels.  Contains timestamps writting in varying formats which are challenging to parse.

title: Brain Bodyweight
summary: A set of brainweight vs bodyweight measures for different species.  Includes extinct species which don't correlate well with contemporary animals.

title: Child Variants
summary: Genomic variants from a clinical study.  Has numerous opportunites for filtering and quantitative exploration.

title: Childrens Hobbies During Lockdown
summary: A pair of datasets quantitating different activities (indoor and outdoor) which can be merged together. Some problems with the calculation of annotated percentage values

title: Cuttlefish Buoyancy
summary: Testing the effect of ocean acidification and feeding on cuttlefish buoyancy. A small dataset but with many quantitative measurements and a few potential confounding factors. Gives lots of opportunity to explore the relationships between measurements and which factors have relevant influence.

title: Modern Pollen Plant Diversity Relationships
summary: Looking at the evolutionary histories of woodland and herbacious plants.  A dataset with lots of different quantitative variables with complex relationships. Long field names can be shortende.  Contains some genetic information as well as environmental and biological measures

title: Neutrophils
summary: White blood cell levels in response to stimulus with different chemicals.  A very small simple quantitative dataset containing unparied replicates and no additional annotation.  Useful for initial quantitative data exploration and plotting.

title: Plant CO2 Uptake
summary: Measuring the amount of CO2 uptake from different plant species at different temperatures. A small complete dataset with a couple of relevant factors.

title: Sleep Deprivation CSD
summary: Measuring the effect of sleep deprevation on migraine induction and Cortical Spreading Depolaraisation in rats. Has an inappropriate mean calculation which generates huge standard deviations.
